00:50:58,059 --> 00:50:59,659
[SPEAKER_00] krizni stožer u opće Nimotski,

1583
00:50:59,659 --> 00:51:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] bio sam njegov član i pokušavao

1584
00:51:01,400 --> 00:51:03,380
[SPEAKER_00] sudjelovati organiziranje vojske

1585
00:51:03,380 --> 00:51:05,460
[SPEAKER_00] i tada sam naučio što znači

1586
00:51:05,460 --> 00:51:07,619
[SPEAKER_00] taj čimbenik

1587
00:51:07,619 --> 00:51:09,400
[SPEAKER_00] za nacionalnu sigurnost,

1588
00:51:09,400 --> 00:51:11,059
[SPEAKER_00] dakle i zbog toga bih danas

1589
00:51:11,059 --> 00:51:12,780
[SPEAKER_00] u ovim dramatičnim trenucima,

1590
00:51:12,780 --> 00:51:14,360
[SPEAKER_00] trenucima kad smo, kažem,

1591
00:51:14,360 --> 00:51:16,760
[SPEAKER_00] ono što smo kazali na početku kad nam prijeti,

1592
00:51:17,119 --> 00:51:20,159
[SPEAKER_00] ili smo već usred specifičnog trećeg svjetskog rata,

1593
00:51:20,159 --> 00:51:22,760
[SPEAKER_00] bio bih, dakle, za uvođenje vojnog roka,

1594
00:51:22,760 --> 00:51:24,139
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, na način na koji to

1595
00:51:24,139 --> 00:51:28,539
[SPEAKER_00] osmisle i propišu stručnjaci, dakle,

1596
00:51:28,539 --> 00:51:29,519
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi koji su od struke,

1597
00:51:29,519 --> 00:51:31,079
[SPEAKER_00] jer ja sam to nisam,

1598
00:51:31,079 --> 00:51:34,719
[SPEAKER_00] jer ta vojska ne služi samo ratovanju,

1599
00:51:34,719 --> 00:51:37,340
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ona ne služi samo pucanju i ubijanju,

1600
00:51:37,460 --> 00:51:39,840
[SPEAKER_00] nego služi i odvraćanju protivnika.

1601
00:51:39,840 --> 00:51:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ono, kad vi imate vojsku,

1602
00:51:41,920 --> 00:51:44,239
[SPEAKER_00] kad imate snagu koja vas štiti,

1603
00:51:44,239 --> 00:51:46,320
[SPEAKER_00] onda se i vaši argumenti za stolom

1604
00:51:46,320 --> 00:51:47,760
[SPEAKER_00] slušaju malo drugačije.

1605
00:51:47,760 --> 00:51:50,179
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, da bi se vaše riječi čule,

1606
00:51:50,179 --> 00:51:52,159
[SPEAKER_00] iza njih moraju stajati

1607
00:51:52,159 --> 00:51:54,739
[SPEAKER_00] ono kolokvijalno kazano topol.

1608
00:51:54,739 --> 00:51:55,219
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1609
00:51:55,219 --> 00:51:57,139
[SPEAKER_01] Gospodin Jovnić, hvala.

1610
00:51:57,139 --> 00:51:59,500
[SPEAKER_00] Čušpezu je došao kraj ove epizodi.

1611
00:51:59,500 --> 00:52:01,699
[SPEAKER_01] Vama želim puno sreće na izborima

1612
00:52:01,699 --> 00:52:03,800
[SPEAKER_01] i nadam se da ćemo sve još vidjeti.

1613
00:52:03,800 --> 00:52:05,880
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala vam na poziv i hvala vam na dobrim željama.

1614
00:52:06,019 --> 00:52:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] Srdečan pozdrav svim gledima.

